SPELL NAME  : Cause critical wounds
SPELL SYNTAX: -Ccw <target>
SPELL COST  : 55 SP
DESCRIPTION : The devoted cleric has the power to call upon the power of Mitra
	      to inflict damage, as well as to heal it. By force of will
	      and through the cleric's devotion, Mitra will inflict terrible
	      wounds upon the target of her wrath.
